# Answer Engine Backend

Minimal FastAPI backend scaffold for local development.

## Local install

```powershell
pip install -e .
```

## Run

```powershell
python -m uvicorn answer_engine_backend.main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8761 --reload
```
